did.unittitle:
Mrs. Jane A. Hope, Hampton, to Miss
                     Campbell, [Washington City]; 
                     21 October 1851.

scopecontent.p:
Description of Cuba; his 23rd birthday;
                     expressions of great affection for his mother;
                     enclosing a poem (now lost.)

Mentions General Johnson, "the Manassas man";
                     Generals Lee and Magruder; his own children Jamie
                     and Anne.
